    /**
     * msg : 资讯详情获取成功
     * code : 1
     * data : {"addTime":"2021-04-12 15:05","author":"品宣部","cid":"1","content":"<p style=\"margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">人的一生有1/3在睡眠中度过，睡姿对健康的影响很大。经常听人说，左侧卧睡觉会压到心脏，这是真的吗？<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/><\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">北京医院心内科副主任医师施海峰2021年1月在健康时报刊文表示，人类的心脏被肋骨组成的胸廓完美地保护起来，即使偶尔受到外界暴力击打都不会造成心脏实质性损害。所谓睡觉的时候左侧卧会压迫心脏，这种说法是错误的。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><br/><\/p><p style=\"margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">到底睡觉应该怎么躺才最好？<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/><\/span><\/p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"http://gzhealthy.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/2409625286593858.jpeg\" title=\"1618280746990099395.jpeg\" alt=\"5cc79e29a3104842e4ab5c96.jpeg\"/><\/p><hr/><p><br/><\/p><section><section><section><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">两类人建议右侧卧睡<\/span><\/strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p><\/section><\/section><\/section><section><section><section><br/><\/section><section><section><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">1.<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">大部分的心脏病人<\/strong><\/span><\/p><\/section><section><p style=\"margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 20px; b 2021-05-11 16:42:33.021 18573-18828/com.gzhealthy.health E/CustomResponseBodyConverter: /p><p style=\"margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">人体心脏并不是位于正中间，而是1/3在偏右，2/3在偏左。北京医院心内科副主任医师施海峰表示，左侧卧位时，由于心脏位于身体中线（重心）下方，这时有更多的血液因为重力作用回到心脏，心脏的负担就比右侧卧位更大。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/><\/p><p style=\"margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">所以心脏病患者为了减轻心脏负担，建议采用右侧卧位。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/><\/p><p style=\"margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">同样的道理，如果心脏病患者上半身抬高，下肢下垂，可以进一步减少回心血量，从而减轻心脏的负担。这也是为什么，很多心衰患者睡觉躺不下来、感觉不舒服，必须要半坐着才行。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/><\/span><\/p><\/section><\/section><section><section><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">2.<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">有胃炎、消化功能差的人<\/strong><\/span><\/p><\/section><section><p style=\"margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">江苏省扬州市第一人民医院消化内科副主任医师支杰华2020年在个人平台发文表示，我们的胃部在整个腹部的上面，而且位置偏左，对于一些胃部有炎症、消化功能低下的人，建议采取右侧卧位，有助于胃内食物的吸收和消化。<\/span><\/p><\/section><\/section><\/section><\/section><p><br/><\/p><p style=\"margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><br/><\/p><hr/><p><br/><\/p><section><section><section><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-wor 2021-05-11 16:42:33.021 18573-18828/com.gzhealthy.health E/CustomResponseBodyConverter: \">&nbsp;反酸烧心的人<\/strong><\/span><\/p><\/section><section><p style=\"margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">对于有烧心、反酸的胃食管反流病患者而言，倾斜左侧卧位可缓解症状。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/><\/p><p style=\"margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">北京大学人民医院胃肠外科刘凡2019年在健康时报刊文表示，睡觉时采用抬高头部的体位或抬高床头、使用床楔等方法能加快酸消除，减少9%~52%的食管酸暴露时间；同时，左侧卧位能减少反流事件的发生，降低13%~76%的食管酸暴露时间。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/><\/span><\/p><\/section><\/section><section><section><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">2.<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">胃酸过多的人<\/strong><\/span><\/p><\/section><section><p style=\"margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">胃酸分泌过多者也是建议采取左侧卧位进行休息。江苏省扬州市第一人民医院消化内科副主任医师支杰华表示，假如朝右侧休息，会导致食管的位置比胃部低，胃酸反流入食管腔内，可能会引起患者出现呛咳甚至窒息。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;\"><br/><\/p><p style=\"margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">而且胃酸分泌过多还容易造成胃部的不适，所以建议胃酸分泌过多的人尽量选择朝左边休息，可以很好地加速胃酸流入消化道里。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/><\/span><\/p><\/section><\/section><\/section><\/section><section><section><section><section><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">3.<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word 2021-05-11 16:42:33.021 18573-18828/com.gzhealthy.health E/CustomResponseBodyConverter: pan><\/p><p style=\"margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/><\/p><p style=\"margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">也不建议右侧卧位。因为怀孕中晚期，增大的子宫呈右旋状态，会压迫右侧输尿管，导致输尿管扩张，甚至肾积水。<\/span><\/p><\/section><\/section><\/section><\/section><p><br/><\/p><p style=\"margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><\/span><\/p><hr/><p><br/><\/p><section><section><section><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">三类人建议仰卧睡<\/span><\/strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p><\/section><section><br/><\/section><section><section><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">1.<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">有脑血栓的人<\/strong><\/span><\/p><\/section><section><p style=\"margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">解放军总医院神经外科主任医师毛之奇2019年在健康时报表示，脑血栓最佳睡姿是仰卧，枕头最好高5厘米，不宜过高或过低，以保证颈动脉不受压迫，使脑部供血充足，这样有利于病情的恢复。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/><\/p><p style=\"margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">侧卧可能会加重血液循环障碍，特别是颈部血流速度减慢，容易在动脉内膜损伤处逐渐聚集而形成血栓。为消除这一隐患，仰卧睡眠较为妥当。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/><\/span><\/p><\/section><\/section><section><section><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">2.<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: bord 2021-05-11 16:42:33.021 18573-18828/com.gzhealthy.health E/CustomResponseBodyConverter: box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">上海东方医院骨科医师袁锋2019年在健康时报表示，从关节健康的角度来说，推荐仰卧。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/><\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">因为仰卧位身体的受力面积最大，不容易对局部造成压迫。蜷着睡容易腿伸不直，侧卧可能肩袖撕裂，抱着睡可能损伤手臂神经。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/><\/span><\/p><\/section><\/section><\/section><\/section><section><section><section><section><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">3.<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">腰间盘突出的人<\/strong><\/span><\/p><\/section><section><p style=\"margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">扬州大学附属医院骨科副主任医师时代2020年在个人平台发文表示，对于腰椎间盘突出的患者而言，仰卧睡觉能有效缓解腰部的不适。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/><\/p><p style=\"margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">当我们平躺时，脖子能保持一定的生理弧度，腰部能紧紧地贴着床，上肢的血液循环会更加畅通，不会感到麻木，腰椎能更加舒适，长此以往腰椎间盘突出就会有所改善，疼痛发作的次数会越来越少。<\/span><\/p><\/section><\/section><\/section><\/section><p><br/><\/p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"http://gzhealthy.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/2344813183047619.gif\" title=\"1618215934866018855.gif\" alt=\"封底.gif\"/><\/p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/><\/p>","id":37,"imageInput":"1618211109788775013.jpeg","isCollection":0,"sort":0,"status":true,"synopsis":"经常听人说，左侧卧睡觉会压到心脏，这是真的吗？","title":"左侧卧睡觉会压到心脏？到底应该朝哪睡？","visit":"860"}
     */

